channel.title: Tech Art Corner :: Unreal Metadata Editor Documentation
channel.description: This plugin has been brought to you by Tech Art Corner. I hope it will serve you well, And you will no longer be irritated by lack of some simple metadata editor that does not require scripting or creating a node graph to just add a simple tag to an asset. I’m open to feedback and if by any chance, this plugin gets popular, I’m looking forward to making it better.
